storing user responses\n\n**Available Functions:**\n- `fetchAllQuizzes()` - Get all quizzes ordered by creation date (DESC)\n- `fetchQuiz(id)` - Get single quiz\n- `createQuiz(data)` - Create new quiz\n- `updateQuiz(id, updates)` - Update quiz\n- `deleteQuiz(id)` - Delete quiz\n- `getQuizResponses(quizId)` - Get all responses for a quiz (admin)\n- `getUserQuizResponse(userId, quizId)` - Get single user response\n- `getUserQuizResults(userId)` - Get user's all quiz results with details\n- `validateQuiz(data)` - Validation helper\n\n---\n\n## 3. Admin Page Patterns\n\n**Admin Pages Location:** `/home/manu/ws_firebase/manuelearning/src/pages/admin/*.astro`\n**Admin Components:** `/home/manu/ws_firebase/manuelearning/src/components/admin-*.js`\n\n**Consistent Pattern Across All Admin Pages:**\n\n1. **Astro Page (.astro)** - Simple shell:\n```astro\n<AdminLayout title=\"...\">\n  <div class=\"admin-section\">\n    <div class=\"admin-section__header\">\n      <h1>Title</h1>\n      <p>Description</p>\n    </div>\n    <admin-component-name></admin-component-name>\n  </div>\n</AdminLayout>\n```\n\n2. **Lit Component (.js)** - Full UI logic using:\n   - Material Symbols Outlined icons\n   - CSS Grid/Flexbox layouts\n   - Form overlays for create/edit\n   - Badge components for metadata\n\n**Badge Pattern (from admin-modules-list.js, lines 750-755):**\n```javascript\n<span class=\"lesson-badge ${lesson.videoUrl ? '' : 'lesson-badge--empty'}\">\n  ${lesson.videoUrl ? 'Video' : 'Sin video'}\n</span>\n<span class=\"lesson-badge ${lesson.documentation ? '' : 'lesson-badge--empty'}\">\n  ${lesson.documentation ? 'Docs' : 'Sin docs'}\n</span>\n```\n\n**Badge Styles:**\n```css\n.lesson-badge {\n  font-size: 0.688rem;\n  padding: 0.125rem 0.5rem;\n  border-radius: 9999px;\n  background: #f0fdf4;\n  color: #166534;\n  font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n.lesson-badge--empty {\n  background: #fef2f2;\n  color: #991b1b;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. Project Structure\n\n### Key Directories:\n```\n/src\n├── pages/\n│   ├── admin/\n│   │   ├── index.astro (dashboard)\n│   │   ├── modules.astro\n│   │   ├── quizzes.astro\n│   │   ├── users.astro\n│   │   ├── cohorts.astro\n│   │   ├── sessions.astro\n│   │   ├── questions.astro\n│   │   ├── retention.astro\n│   │   └── settings.astro\n│   └── ...other pages\n├── components/\n│   ├── admin-modules-list.js (26KB - complex with nested lessons)\n│   ├── admin-quizzes-list.js (14KB - quiz management)\n│   ├── admin-users-list.js\n│   ├── admin-cohorts-list.js\n│   ├── admin-sessions-list.js\n│   ├── admin-questions-list.js\n│   ├── admin-dashboard.js\n│   ├── admin-retention-dashboard.js\n│   ├── lesson-view.js\n│   ├── lesson-nav.js\n│   └── shared/\n│       └── material-icons.js\n├── lib/\n│   ├── firebase/\n│   │   ├── config.js\n│   │   ├── modules.js (Modules + Lessons)\n│   │   ├── quizzes.js (Quizzes + Responses)\n│   │   ├── progress.js\n│   │   ├── users.js\n│   │   ├── sessions.js\n│   │   ├── questions.js\n│   │   ├── cohorts.js\n│   │   └── ...other services\n│   ├── auth-ready.js\n│   ├── search-filter.js\n│   ├── reorder-utils.js\n│   └── ...utilities\n├── layouts/\n│   └── AdminLayout.astro\n└── styles/\n```\n\n---\n\n## 5. Module/Lesson Structure\n\n**File:** `/home/manu/ws_firebase/manuelearning/src/lib/firebase/modules.js`\n\n**Firestore Structure:**\n```\nmodules/\n  {moduleId}/\n    (module document with: title, description, order, createdAt)\n    lessons/ (subcollection)\n      {lessonId}/\n        (lesson document with: title, description, order, videoUrl, documentation, createdAt)\n```\n\n**Key Functions:**\n- `fetchAllModules()` - All modules ordered by order ASC\n- `fetchLessons(moduleId)` - All lessons in a module\n- `fetchLesson(moduleId, lessonId)` - Single lesson\n- `createLesson(moduleId, data)` - Create lesson in module\n- `updateLesson(moduleId, lessonId, updates)` - Update lesson\n- `deleteLesson(moduleId, lessonId)` - Delete lesson\n- `reorderLesson(moduleId, lessons, lessonId, direction)` - Move lesson up/down\n\n---\n\n## 6. Progress Tracking\n\n**File:** `/home/manu/ws_firebase/manuelearning/src/lib/firebase/progress.js`\n\n**Document ID Format:** `{userId}_{moduleId}_{lessonId}`\n\n```javascript\n{\n  userId: string,\n  moduleId: string,\n  lessonId: string,\n  completed: boolean,\n  completedAt: Timestamp\n}\n```\n\n**Key Functions:**\n- `markLessonCompleted(userId, moduleId, lessonId)`\n- `isLessonCompleted(userId, moduleId, lessonId)`\n- `getUserProgress(userId)` - All completed lessons for user\n\n---\n\n## 7. Admin Dashboard Navigation\n\n**Sidebar Navigation** (AdminLayout.astro, lines 47-83):\n- Users\n- Convocatorias (Cohorts)\n- Módulos (Modules + nested lessons admin)\n- Quizzes\n- Sesiones (Sessions)\n- Preguntas (Questions)\n- Retención (Retention)\n- Configuración (Settings)\n- Dashboard (student view)\n\n---\n\n## 8. Recent Commits (Context)\n\n- **f21f3dc** - feat: add quiz editing capability for admin (#24)\n- **20bc493** - feat: add mark lesson as completed button to lesson view (#23)\n- **d7cd611** - refactor: rename \"cohortes\" to \"convocatorias\" across platform (#22)\n- **5dfb3e7** - feat: private questions by default with admin visibility toggle (#21)\n\n---\n\n## 9. Key File Paths Summary\n\n| Purpose | File Path |\n|---------|-----------|\n| Admin Quiz Page | `/src/pages/admin/quizzes.astro` |\n| Quiz List Component | `/src/components/admin-quizzes-list.js` |\n| Quiz Service | `/src/lib/firebase/quizzes.js` |\n| Admin Modules Page | `/src/pages/admin/modules.astro` |\n| Modules+Lessons Comp | `/src/components/admin-modules-list.js` |\n| Modules Service | `/src/lib/firebase/modules.js` |\n| Lesson View Component | `/src/components/lesson-view.js` |\n| Progress Service | `/src/lib/firebase/progress.js` |\n| Admin Layout | `/src/layouts/AdminLayout.astro` |\n| Material Icons | `/src/components/shared/material-icons.js` |\n\n---\n\n## Key Insights for Quiz Indicator Feature\n\n1. **Quiz-Lesson Relationship:** Quizzes store both `moduleId` AND optional `lessonId`, allowing quizzes to be associated with specific lessons or just modules.\n\n2. **Badge Pattern:** The codebase already uses badges extensively (see admin-modules-list.js for \"Video\"/\"Sin video\" and \"Docs\"/\"Sin docs\" examples).\n\n3. **Admin Lesson Access:** Lessons are managed through the modules admin interface, NOT via a dedicated lessons admin page.\n\n4. **No Dedicated Quiz-Lesson Link:** Currently, there's no admin-facing view showing which quizzes are linked to which lessons. This would be the feature to implement.\n\n5. **Expansion Pattern:** The modules component uses expandable cards to show nested lessons - a similar pattern could be used to show quizzes within lessons."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a459bf84db36339a2 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 86552\ntool_uses: 35\nduration_ms: 84954</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"bdd0c713-236c-4c4b-91a1-64825901815d","uuid":"d91ce402-53e6-459e-bc84-eff35414fcbe","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore this codebase to find:\n1. The admin lesson listing page/component (look in src/pages/admin or similar)\n2. How quizzes are stored and related to lessons (look for quiz-related files, services, Firestore collections)\n3. Existing patterns for admin pages - how they load data, display lists, use icons/badges\n4. The project structure (Astro, Lit, Firebase based)\n\nBe very thorough - check src/pages/admin/*, src/components/admin/*, src/services/*, and any quiz-related files. Show me the content of the admin lesson listing and quiz service files.","agentId":"a459bf84db36339a2","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information needed. Let me compile a comprehensive report.\n\n---\n\n## Codebase Exploration Report: ManuElearning Admin Quiz Indicator\n\n### Project Overview\n**Stack:** Astro + Lit Web Components + Firebase (Firestore + Auth)\n**Current Branch:** `fea